      "key": "fr08_marmot_2",
      "nodeTitle": "marmot",
      "sourceText": "Dorm toată iarna sub zăpadă. Asta se numește hibernare!",
      "sourceEnText": "I sleep all winter under the snow. This is called hibernation!",
